comment: McCollum (POR) sets the screen on Clarkson (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Young (LAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Young (LAL) makes incidental contact with Plumlee (POR) during rebounding.
Williams (LAL) maintains legal guarding position on Turner (POR) in the post.
Williams (LAL) makes contact with Turner's (POR) arm that affects his ability control the pass.
Clarkson (LAL) maintains legal guarding position on Lillard (POR) on the perimeter.
[Observable in enhanced video] Plumlee (POR) never fully clears the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Zubac (LAL) sets the screen on Lillard (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Plumlee (POR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Clarkson (LAL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Young (LAL) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Aminu (POR) legally contests Deng's (LAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
